      <title>欧元区通货膨胀停留在2％以上可能会使欧洲央行的结果保持开放</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/euro-zone-inflation-stuck-above-2-may-keep-ecb-outcome-open</link>
